I don't know.

00:08:18.980 --> 00:08:19.980
What the hell.

00:08:19.980 --> 00:08:20.980
&gt;&gt;Interviewer: Alright.

00:08:20.980 --> 00:08:21.980
I'll, I'll ask him.

00:08:21.980 --> 00:08:22.980
&gt;&gt;Jonah Hill: I flew down to northern California.

00:08:22.980 --> 00:08:23.980
Don't ask me about Seth.

00:08:23.980 --> 00:08:24.980
He's great.

00:08:24.980 --> 00:08:26.860
He's getting married in a couple of weeks,
I'm gonna go to his wedding.

00:08:26.860 --> 00:08:27.860
&gt;&gt;Interviewer: Excellent.

