00:11:33.970 --> 00:11:38.850
empty and then you know you can run around
the bases and throw the ball around and stuff

00:11:38.850 --> 00:11:43.520
and then when we shot a lot of the games that
are really factual about what actually took

00:11:43.520 --> 00:11:49.510
place, there were real A's fans in the stadium,
some of whom were at those actual games and

00:11:49.510 --> 00:11:53.600
that was really cool, you know, that was really
exciting.

